A yearly trip to visit Uncle Tom and his wishing well ends in heartbreak for twin siblings Joe and Emma when their mom up and leaves in the middle of the night.

The next year, Joe is determined to get the spirits of the wishing well to help him locate his absent mom. But when he learns what's in the well, he'll wish he never went looking.

